location: 5455 Avenue de Gaspé #200, Montréal, QC H2T 3B3
title: Inner workings of a JavaScript Framework

datas.title: Why do we need a front-end framework, and how does it work?
datas.author: f3ltron
datas.description: This talk will explore how a basic JavaScript framework works and how easy it can be to create a simple one. We will also see why you should not do create your own framework.

datas.title: From Vuejs template tag to HTML, how does it work?
datas.author: tlebel
datas.description: This talk will explore how Vue.js transforms the template tag in a Vue single file component into HTML.
